  <brief_title>Totally Implantable Venous Access Devices: Quality of Life and Body Image</brief_title>
  <acronym>BI-PORT</acronym>
  <official_title>Totally Implantable Venous Access Devices (TIVAD): Impact on Quality of Life and Body Image</official_title>
