    <description>cognitive/behavioural intervention (6 times starting from hospital admission, in 90 days; for arm of intervention)
metacognitive techniques (6 times starting from hospital admission, in 90 days; for arm of intervention)
psychoeducational intervention (6 times starting from hospital admission; for arm of intervention)
questionnaires: EORTC questionnaires and a written structured interview (3 times: hospital admission,15 days after surgical intervention, 90 days after intervention; in both arms)</description>
